[Student "S"]
{EAST has 13 points but has no bid over 1\D. 
WEST can make a Takeout Double, so he does.

EAST now cue-bids \D to show opening hand strength.

WEST shows his \H suit, EAST doesn't like it. 
EAST shows her \S suit, WEST doesn't like it. 
WEST shows his \C suit, EAST likes it fine, but decides 3NT will be easier than 5\C.}

