[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 12 points, but with two 5-card suits worthy of an overcall. There isn't really a 
right and wrong here, but it usually works out best to overcall in the higher-ranking suit. That 
leaves open the possibility of bidding the second suit later.

In this Deal, after NORTH overcalls 1\S, that later possibility never happens because 
everybody should pass.}

